01:24:07,000 --> 01:24:08,333
<font color="#ffff00">Ayo pergi.</font>

1001
01:24:09,125 --> 01:24:10,625
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tidak mau pulang.</font>

1002
01:24:12,458 --> 01:24:14,042
<font color="#ffff00">- Baiklah.
