1003
01:25:20,292 --> 01:25:21,542
<font color="#ffff00">Aku harus ke kamar mandi.</font>

1004
01:25:22,625 --> 01:25:23,708
<font color="#ffff00">Baiklah.</font>

1005
01:26:00,417 --> 01:26:01,625
<font color="#ffff00">Liu Chunhe!</font>

1006
01:26:34,458 --> 01:26:37,500
<font color="#ffff00">"Kau bintang di atas awan."</font>

1007
01:26:40,000 --> 01:26:44,000
<font color="#ffff00">Aku orang aneh yang menyeberangi
