1021
01:28:04,500 --> 01:28:06,542
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan cemas.</font>

1022
01:28:07,042 --> 01:28:08,417
<font color="#ffff00">Aku melihatnya di sini.</font>

1023
01:28:14,208 --> 01:28:16,375
<font color="#ffff00">Aku harus pergi. Dah.</font>

1024
01:28:20,167 --> 01:28:21,333
<font color="#ffff00">Kau sudah pulang.</font>

1025
01:28:22,333 --> 01:28:24,333
<font color="#ffff00">- Ya.
