1026
01:28:25,583 --> 01:28:28,250
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak. Aku sudah makan.</font>

1027
01:28:33,833 --> 01:28:34,958
<font color="#ffff00">Apa ini?</font>

1028
01:28:37,167 --> 01:28:38,708
<font color="#ffff00">Hadiah untuk Ibu.</font>

1029
01:28:39,625 --> 01:28:41,042
<font color="#ffff00">Untuk ibumu?</font>

1030
01:28:41,125 --> 01:28:43,500
<font color="#ffff00">- Apa isinya?
- Permen buatanku.</font>

1031
01:28:44,958 --> 01:28:47,167
<font color="#ffff00">- Kau membuatnya?
- Ya.</font>

1032
01:28:52,208 --> 01:28:53,625
<font color="#ffff00">Kau membuat ini!</font>

1033
01:29:00,292 --> 01:29:01,625
<font color="#ffff00">Lezat.</font>

1034
01:29:01,708 --> 01:29:03,625
<font color="#ffff00">Gula darah ibumu masih sangat tinggi.</font>

1035
01:29:04,292 --> 01:29:05,692
<font color="#ffff00">Dia tidak bisa makan makanan manis.</font>

1036
01:29:10,583 --> 01:29:12,000
<font color="#ffff00">Sangat indah!</font>

1037
01:29:12,500 --> 01:29:13,875
<font color="#ffff00">Nak.</font>

1038
01:29:13,958 --> 01:29:15,792
<font color="#ffff00">Kau sangat pandai!</font>

1039
01:29:16,875 --> 01:29:18,208
<font color="#ffff00">Bau apa ini?</font>

1040
01:29:19,750 --> 01:29:21,250
<font color="#ffff00">Sup kaki babi Nenek!</font>

1041
01:32:26,125 --> 01:32:27,250
<font color="#ffff00">Ada apa, Nak?</font>

1042
01:32:28,125 --> 01:32:30,458
<font color="#ffff00">Chunhe! Apa yang terjadi?</font>

1043
