<font color="#ffff00">Kenapa kau menjejali mulutmu? Chunhe!</font>

1044
01:32:34,417 --> 01:32:35,417
<font color="#ffff00">Buka!</font>

1045
01:32:36,375 --> 01:32:38,750
<font color="#ffff00">Apa yang kau lakukan? Kau gila!</font>

1046
01:32:39,542 --> 01:32:41,417
<font color="#ffff00">Apa yang kau lakukan? Chunhe…</font>

1047
01:32:42,292 --> 01:32:44,417
<font color="#ffff00">Chunhe!</font>

1048
01:32:47,958 --> 01:32:49,042
<font color="#ffff00">Chunhe!</font>

1049
01:32:51,667 --> 01:32:53,792
<font color="#ffff00">Apa kau gila? Buka mulutmu!</font>

1050
01:32:53,875 --> 01:32:55,875
<font color="#ffff00">Muntahkan!</font>

1051
01:34:22,167 --> 01:34:25,167
<font color="#ffff00">- Chunhe!
