1058
01:36:21,167 --> 01:36:23,458
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan bicara.</font>

1059
01:36:24,417 --> 01:36:26,042
<font color="#ffff00">Saat kau sedang diselamatkan,</font>

1060
01:36:27,833 --> 01:36:29,375
<font color="#ffff00">mereka memotong trakeamu.</font>

1061
01:36:31,375 --> 01:36:33,542
<font color="#ffff00">Butuh waktu agar lukanya sembuh.</font>

1062
01:36:41,250 --> 01:36:42,333
<font color="#ffff00">Baru-baru ini,</font>

1063
01:36:43,583 --> 01:36:46,458
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu memimpikan kelahiranmu.</font>

1064
01:36:50,708 --> 01:36:53,958
<font color="#ffff00">Tiga dokter menekan perut Ibu
