1065
01:36:56,042 --> 01:36:57,417
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu mengejan</font>

1066
01:36:58,708 --> 01:37:00,167
<font color="#ffff00">sekuat yang Ibu mampu.</font>

1067
01:37:02,333 --> 01:37:04,000
<font color="#ffff00">Tapi Ibu selalu saja salah.</font>

1068
01:37:06,292 --> 01:37:07,583
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka bilang</font>

1069
01:37:08,958 --> 01:37:10,292
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu tidak tahu cara mengejan.</font>

1070
01:37:15,708 --> 01:37:17,000
<font color="#ffff00">Selama ini,</font>

1071
01:37:19,042 --> 01:37:20,708
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu tidak bisa merayakan ulang tahunmu</font>

1072
01:37:23,458 --> 01:37:25,417
<font color="#ffff00">dan memberimu kartu disabilitas</font>

1073
01:37:29,458 --> 01:37:31,125
<font color="#ffff00">karena Ibu terngiang ucapan itu.</font>

1074
01:37:32,875 --> 01:37:35,125
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu masih teringat saat melahirkan adikmu.</font>

1075
01:37:37,708 --> 01:37:39,583
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu ingat salah mengejan.</font>

1076
01:37:41,875 --> 01:37:44,333
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu cemas mengulangi kesalahan.</font>

1077
01:37:46,250 --> 01:37:47,250
<font color="#ffff00">Chunhe.</font>

1078
01:37:50,458 --> 01:37:51,875
<font color="#ffff00">Hari itu, Ibu tidak bermaksud</font>

1079
01:37:53,250 --> 01:37:54,708
<font color="#ffff00">menjauhkanmu.</font>

1080
01:37:57,042 --> 01:37:58,333
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu gelisah.</font>

1081
01:37:59,750 --> 01:38:01,000
<font color="#ffff00">Takut.</font>

1082
01:38:04,667 --> 01:38:05,833
<font color="#ffff00">Ini</font>

1083
01:38:07,583 --> 01:38:10,542
<font color="#ffff00">kesempatan terakhir Ibu
menjadi seorang ibu.</font>

1084
01:38:12,708 --> 01:38:15,125
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu tidak mau menyesal.</font>

1085
01:38:17,000 --> 01:38:18,083
<font color="#ffff00">Chunhe.</font>

1086
01:38:20,208 --> 01:38:22,083
<font color="#ffff00">Maaf.</font>

1087
01:38:25,708 --> 01:38:28,708
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu sungguh minta maaf. Chunhe.</font>

1088
01:39:08,125 --> 01:39:09,125
<font color="#ffff00">Berlutut.</font>

1089
01:39:13,750 --> 01:39:16,083
<font color="#ffff00">Dewa Perang! Biasanya aku memerankanmu.</font>

1090
01:39:16,167 --> 01:39:19,833
<font color="#ffff00">Hari ini aku menjadi dirimu.</font>

1091
01:39:34,500 --> 01:39:38,250
<font color="#ffff00">Lewati jubah Dewa Perang.</font>

1092
01:39:38,333 --> 01:39:43,083
<font color="#ffff00">Kau akan melewati semua rintangan
