01:40:44,583 --> 01:40:47,458
<font color="#ffff00">Kenapa orang tidak bisa menjadi tonggeret?</font>

1095
01:40:48,958 --> 01:40:50,792
<font color="#ffff00">Setiap dia melepaskan cangkangnya,</font>

1096
01:40:52,583 --> 01:40:54,875
<font color="#ffff00">ia punya kehidupan baru.</font>

1097
01:41:46,167 --> 01:41:47,167
<font color="#ffff00">Kau bisa lakukan.</font>

1098
01:43:22,125 --> 01:43:23,208
<font color="#ffff00">Nak?</font>

1099
01:43:30,208 --> 01:43:31,375
<font color="#ffff00">Kenapa kau tidak tidur?</font>

1100
01:43:51,292 --> 01:43:54,042
<font color="#ffff00">Apa di sini sakit?</font>

1101
01:43:57,958 --> 01:43:59,208
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak.</font>

1102
01:44:00,792 --> 01:44:02,083
<font color="#ffff00">Hanya sensitif terhadap angin.</font>

1103
01:44:07,708 --> 01:44:09,208
<font color="#ffff00">Nenek tidak pernah memberitahuku</font>

1104
01:44:11,125 --> 01:44:13,167
<font color="#ffff00">asal luka itu.</font>

1105
01:44:16,917 --> 01:44:19,792
<font color="#ffff00">Saat pergi ke Tibet,</font>

1106
01:44:19,875 --> 01:44:21,083
<font color="#ffff00">Nenek membuka restoran.</font>

1107
01:44:22,708 --> 01:44:24,417
<font color="#ffff00">Nenek sedang mengerjakan pembukuan.</font>

1108
01:44:27,750 --> 01:44:28,958
<font color="#ffff00">Pisau sepanjang ini</font>

