1127
01:46:00,292 --> 01:46:02,417
<font color="#ffff00">Nenek melahirkan dia saat 21 tahun.</font>

1128
01:46:06,292 --> 01:46:07,500
<font color="#ffff00">Sebulan kemudian,</font>

1129
01:46:08,542 --> 01:46:10,000
<font color="#ffff00">ayahnya meninggalkan Nenek</font>

1130
01:46:11,500 --> 01:46:12,875
<font color="#ffff00">demi orang lain.</font>

1131
01:46:17,375 --> 01:46:21,042
<font color="#ffff00">Nenek pergi ke Tibet sendirian
